                        <condition key="deficient">Most probably a part of the Ms. is missing and
                           some fols. are misplaced. 
 Back board and a part of the front board
                           are missing.
 The Ms. has been resewn on the 2nd and 3rd sewing
                           stations. The sewing is partly damaged.
 Many fols. are affected by
                           water. 
 Holes are carefully amended on <locus target="#26">26</locus>, 29, 34, 35.</condition>
